reviews.review_text:
This one is best Best of the 3 nights as far as positioning by taper. I think he found his groove at these shows during Peggy O on the 27th and the recordings get better and better. 
 I would burn this show for sure to listen to in my car. All 3 of these nights were epic to me. being my 1st year at Red Rocks.  Thank you for the hard work on making these available to us all.  Maybe you could post the Keil show on 8 3 82. There are no aud recordings here of that one.
Great show, great place, great sound Thanks for the upload!!
